short_summary: Multiple Victoria-Class Spares for replacement of Line Feed Lines
description: The Department of National Defence desires to purchase from eligible sources multiple spares for the Line Feeds of Victoria-Class warships. The tender must be submitted at the following addresses: 101 Colonel By Dr. Ottawa ON K1A 0K2. If you have difficulty accessing the attachment, please contact Procurement at the email below. Please include your file name and browsing details so we can provide accurate browser not found errors.
